---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Physician Training" description="RACP Basic Training program overview for physicians and paediatricians.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Physician Training</h1>
    <p>RACP — Royal Australasian College of Physicians · Basic Training Program</p>
  </div>

  <div class="stat-grid">
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">36</div><div class="stat-label">months FTE clinical experience required</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">49</div><div class="stat-label">competencies across 10 domains</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">8</div><div class="stat-label">Entrustable Professional Activities</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">3</div><div class="stat-label">training phases to complete</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Training Phases</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Foundation</div>
      <p>Entry point of training. Submit your application by 28 Feb or 31 Aug.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Consolidation</div>
      <p>Ongoing rotations and work-based assessments. 12 learning captures + 12 observation captures per phase.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Completion</div>
      <p>Written Examination (early) and Clinical Examination (mid-phase). Final phase before fellowship.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Quick Links</h2>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li><a href="/entry">Entry requirements & selection criteria</a></li>
      <li><a href="/program">Learning, teaching & assessment programs</a></li>
      <li><a href="/curriculum">Curricula standards — competencies, EPAs, knowledge guides</a></li>
      <li><a href="/progression">Learning goals & Be / Do / Know progression scales</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
